<HEADLINE>
THE CHALLENGER: SCHUMER ASSAILS D'AMATO ON GUN CONTROL 
</HEADLINE>
  (DUPLICATION WARNING: also sent in category `p') 
(Eds: Sidebar with NY-CAMPAIGN-DAMATO; see also NY-VALLONE-AD and
NY-PATAKI-AD) 
(nk) 
 By ABBY GOODNOUGH   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK _ Rep. Charles Schumer fiercely criticized Sen. Alfonse
D'Amato's voting record on gun control Sunday, saying the
Republican incumbent was more interested in collecting donations
from the National Rifle Association than protecting the lives of
New Yorkers.
</P>
<P>
   Schumer, a Democrat from Brooklyn, who is hoping to unseat
D'Amato in November, held a news conference in City Hall Park to
