<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-NY-CAMPAIGN-D'AMATO-575&AMP;ADD-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
D'AMATO ASSAILS RIVAL IN UPSTATE SWING 
</HEADLINE>
  (DUPLICATION WARNING: Also filed in category ``a.'') 
(See also: NY-CAMPAIGN-SCHUMER, NY-CAMPAIGN-VALLONE and
NY-CAMPAIGN-PATAKI) 
(lh) 
 By JAMES DAO   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
