   ROSENFELD-SHORTTAKES _ After Salon reported it, Henry Hyde
admitted he had an affair with a married woman 30 years ago. As a
journalistic enterprise, it was enough to make sleaze cringe.
Hyde's stately response, however, may be savored. (Rosenfeld, Cox
News Service) MOVED.
