<HEADLINE>
JAPANESE BANK LOSSES ARE BIGGEST COVER-UP EVER 
</HEADLINE>
   Commentary  
 (EDS: Filed in ``i'' and ``f'' categories)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By BERNARD D. KAPLAN  
 c.1998 Hearst Newspapers  
<TEXT>
