   SENT TO: category codes ``l'' lifestyle news and ``a'' general
news.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; AN OCEAN OF SELTZER &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; (700 words) &QL; 
 &UR; ONE B&AMP;W SLIDE &QL; 
 &UR; By KATHY A SVITIL &LR;  &QC;
</P>
<P>
   Jupiter's moon Europa continues to surprise scientists. First
there was evidence of an ocean beneath miles of ice. Now it appears
that the ocean is carbonated. Kathy A. Svitil is an associate
editor for Discover magazine.
</P>
