   MUSIC-POP (Undated) _ Bette Midler's new album has a couple of
awkward moments, but for the most part, her so-called ``cosmic
fabulosity'' is on full, mind-expanding display. By Steve Morse.
</P>
<P>
   BOOK-MODEL (Undated) _ Jay McInerney's ``Model Behavior''
suffers from glossy cleverness; the au courant indifference that
seeps from its pages feels more hollow than sad. By Gail Caldwell.
</P>
<P>
   BOOKS-LINDBERGH (Undated) _ Two new biographies explore Charles
A. Lindbergh's ultimate American life. By David M. Shribman. 1500
words.
</P>
