   SCIENCE
</P>
<P>
   SUPERSTRINGS/Diagram -- 50p x 14 -- (BC-SCI-SUPERSTRINGS-NYT)
</P>
<P>
   Comprehensive diagram detailing the theory of superstrings.
</P>
