situation remains unsettled. But Bynum's field goals of 19 and 23
yards recently in A&AMP;M's 28-7 victory over Louisiana Tech have left
him feeling better about himself. And, he hopes, it has the Aggies
feeling better about him, too. (Riggs, Austin American-Statesman)
MOVED.
