Series in Stuart this July, it was supposed to be the pinnacle of
their year. Instead, within two days of the tournament's opening
ceremony on July 27, two mothers had been arrested for passing a
counterfeit $20 at a concession stand. (Mnookin, Palm Beach Post)
MOVED.
