   THE CLINTON CRISIS
</P>
<P>
   ATTN NEWS EDS: CoxNet will produce two full pages on today's
events regarding the release of Clinton testimony material. They
will incorporate many of the following stories, as well as some
excerpts if appropriate, and AP photos. They will not include a
lead Clinton wrapup, so can be used as jump pages/inside pages.
They will be posted on the Cox server by 7 p.m. Eastern time. For
more information, please call CoxNet at 404-526-5456.
