</P>
<P>
   CARIBBEAN-HURRICANE _ MIAMI _ A wrap on Hurricane George, as it
barrels into the northeastern Caribbean with 110 mph winds today,
flooding roads, toppling trees and utility lines and forcing
thousands from their homes. After pummeling the Leeward islands on
Sunday, it moved on to the Virgin Islands and uerto Rico. It is
still too early to say when and if it will hit the United States,
but the U.S. National Hurricane Center warned the storm was
``extremely dangerous.'' Developing. (Emling, Cox News Service).
ETA: 5 p.m.
</P>
