<HEADLINE>
STUDENTS CRITICIZE QUESTIONS AS WELL AS ANSWERS 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Repeating for all needing.)  (See also: CLINTON-RDP, CLINTON-ASSESS, CLINTON-KOHL,
CLINTON-PERJURY, CLINTON-IMAGE, CLINTON-CONGRESS, CLINTON-MONICA,
CLINTON-DAY, CLINTON-TACTIC, CLINTON-WATCH-NY,
CLINTON-WATCH-SEATTLE, CLINTON-WATCH-DENVER, CLINTON-TV-REVIEW,
CLINTON-MEDIA, CLINTON-EVIDENCE, CLINTON-MONICA-TEXT,
CLINTON-LETTERS-TEXT) 
(lb) 
 By RICK BRAGG   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ It might have been from emotion or it might have been
the color control on the itty-bitty television, but President
