   &UR;  &LR;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; NATIONAL (a) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   FEDS-ARREST (Boston) -- He's viewed by law enforcement as the
would-be successor to reputed mobster Whitey Bulger's empire: Phil
Myers, who earned a reputation for viciousness when he killed a
fellow inmate in prison, is arrested by federal agents. By Shelley
Murphy and Patricia Nealon. 1000 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; FINANCIAL (f) &LR;
</P>
